OL,4,CLloyds Bank bans Bitcoin purchases
OL,5, Lloyds Banking Group has banned its
OL,6, customers from buying Bitcoin and other
OL,7, crypto-currencies on their credit
OL,8, cards.
OL,10,FThe ban, starting on Monday, applies to
OL,11,FLloyds Bank, Bank of Scotland, Halifax
OL,12,Fand MBNA customers. 
OL,14,FIt will not apply to debit cards, only
OL,15,Fto the banking group's eight million
OL,16,Fcredit card customers.
OL,18,FThe move follows a sharp fall in the
OL,19,Fvalue of digital currencies, prompting
OL,20,Ffears about people running up debts.
